			<div class="col-lg-6">
				<div class="about_content">
					<div class="about_text">
						<p>RB Community is a church located in north San Diego within the beautiful suburbs of Rancho
							Bernardo. We draw our faith family from surrounding neighborhoods of Poway, Del Sur,
							Escondido, 4S Ranch and PQ. With a 50 year legacy of generosity to our neighbors, we
							continue to embrace Biblical principles and compassionate service in the name of Jesus.</p>
						<p>We offer 6 worship services every weekend, in a variety of styles. Adult education options
							run throughout the week, and service opportunities for all ages run throughout the year. We
							have a unique preschool recognized for its inclusivity for children of all abilities, and we
							are blessed with a stunning campus of multiple buildings for worship, family ministries,
							fellowship and community programs. There are things happening every day of the week at RB
							Community.</p>
						<p>We have a large staff to cover all our programming, including pastors with doctoral degrees
							and advanced seminary training. Our members are active in a variety of events that impact
							the community and bless the world. Our vision is grounded in the words of Jesus, “From the
							believers shall flow rivers of living water.” John 7:38. In short, we believe encounters
							with Jesus transform lives.</p>
						<p>We invite you to worship, or to ask questions – see for yourself if God is calling you to our
							family.</p>
					</div>
